{"tid":459852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真勇武] 【血洗教堂】居民擸槍與槍手駁火 目擊者：居民「追殺」擊斃槍手","createTime":"2017-11-06T06:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T09:43:07.000Z","uid":51904,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6d241b8cc5d748139e7eb10b345d9d1726f895","tid":459852,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T06:59:07.000Z","msg":"美國德州周日一名男子衝入當地一間教堂亂槍掃射，導致至少26死20傷。26歲槍手凱利（Devin Patrick Kelley）事後駕車逃離現場，警方尋回他時他已中槍身亡，未知是自殺抑或他殺，不過有目擊者指，他是被居民射殺。<br />\n<br />\n一名於教堂附近目擊事件的男子朗根多夫（Johnnie Langendorff）表示，凱利逃離教堂時，一名途人曾與他駁火。凱利後來登上貨車逃離現場，朗根多夫於是與該名途人一起駕車高速尾隨其後，朗根多夫聲稱，是該途人開槍擊斃凱利。<br />\n<br />\n凱利後來向東北方行車，駛至附近的瓜達盧佩縣（Guadalupe County）。警方尋獲凱利時，他的汽車曾撞向路邊，他本人則已中槍身亡，警方未確認他是吞槍自殺還是被途人擊斃。"},{"pid":"2ea8fe54ad515e17f6d3d621478a68210e3a8cf9","tid":459852,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"剃人頭者人亦剃其頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad398e24d9678ef08fc58ecf5273f7f800e6cdc","tid":459852,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"Texas <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2c865142a4a308a8335d81fc00cb4d1354e60d","tid":459852,"uid":33868,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:25:11.000Z","msg":"Kingsman"},{"pid":"e1532b188459abf8a4a6e5dd654d89e4e49abc01","tid":459852,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"「進攻敵人，凱利。」"},{"pid":"94be276bf88f4f077f5a881c077189dc9ec3f403","tid":459852,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:15:49.000Z","msg":"敵將 is doctor lee  (西部牛仔版)"},{"pid":"faea4b361e19e23c1baf8f0dcf1f7341449bfe7e","tid":459852,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"德州牛仔👍"},{"pid":"85b82ff166780a53b81d552f37f4956ee7f8e3ef","tid":459852,"uid":33481,